Now that Bec is halfway through her pregnancy it's time to start thinking about where our little baby will live at our tiny cabin in the woods ü•∞ Head to our link to get 5 travel packs and a FREE one-year supply of vitamin D3K2 drops with your first purchase of AG1 https://drinkag1.com/eamonandbec

Back in 2020, we bought this rundown cabin in the Canadian wilderness to make a family home and create a cozy home base. We are so proud of how far we've come with this (mostly) DIY project and couldn't be happier to be raising a beautiful new baby out here in the woods. Is there honestly anything better than being in nature, getting your toes in the dirt and swimming in Canadian fresh water lakes? The only dilemma is that this cabin is barely big enough for the the 3 of us.... where will we find a spot for baby's stuff?

snippet.title: I Made Minecraft Fun Again
snippet.description:
What Makes Minecraft Fun? I've asked myself this question for a while, and I still haven't figured out the answer. But, I'm gonna change that. I'm not leaving Minecraft until I Make Minecraft Fun Again. 

Discord: https://discord.gg/VeVDgNgv8V

Like ParrotX2 and his LifeSteal SMP Series where he broke bedrock or blew up 2000 TNT. Not Tubbo / TommyInnit / or any other Dream SMP member. This is a new and original Minecraft idea like HermitCraft or LastLife with Grian and MumboJumbo. Survival is harder than Hardcore Minecraft because PVP is on. 

A Minecraft video made by Parrot or ParrotX2 on other platforms! Enjoy! 

Thanks to Slatcho for the help editing: https://linktr.ee/slatcho?utm_source=linktree_admin_share
